{"tid":2190893,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"油麻地後巷發現多袋磚頭及碎石 警方檢走追查物主身分","createTime":"2020-09-06T05:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T06:13:28.000Z","uid":222970,"like":17,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ecdaa5ee940db810ac9585a6d1dc75ee7cc3ae","tid":2190893,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:08:22.000Z","msg":"【油麻地後巷發現多袋磚頭及碎石 警方檢走追查物主身分】<br />\n<br />\n中午約12時，警方在油麻地進行反罪惡巡邏期間，在北海街後巷發現三袋磚頭及碎石。由於有網民發起今日下午在九龍區遊行，並煽動他人走出馬路，更明言要「重燃戰火」，而警方檢獲該批磚頭及碎石的地點與其計劃遊行路線非常接近，警方不排除有人打算在該活動中使用。警方已檢走相關物品進行調查，並會翻查附近閉路電視，以確認物主身分及物品用途。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，上述遊行並無獲得警方的不反對通知書，屬於未經批准集結，如任何人組織或參與該活動，均有可能觸犯《公安條例》，一經定罪最高可被判處監禁5年。<br />\n<br />\n警方現正在相關遊行路線一帶加緊巡邏及截查可疑人，如遇有任何違法行為，必定嚴正執法。警方呼籲前往九龍區的市民留意附近環境及自身安全，如發現任何可疑人或可疑物品，請即向警方舉報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K70dKSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK70dKSo.jpg&h=f15f73fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPp6kqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPp6kqJ.jpg&h=a3903eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fVxfY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fVxfY4.jpg&h=c4566728&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29fa5d0db586bbef1c70eee67cea1f79c7a8e22f","tid":2190893,"uid":57205,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"咁做地盤日日都要報警"},{"pid":"094fee0c1f6a2006a91b386deff0e975198a5973","tid":2190893,"uid":207846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55